        "schemeImageUrl": "",
        "detailedDescription_md": "The scheme “Award to Scheduled Castes Students Who Secured Top Ranks at State and District Level in Standard X &amp;amp; XII” is initiated by the Director Scheduled Caste Welfare, Department of Social Justice &amp;amp; Empowerment, Government of Gujarat. Under the scheme, the Scheduled Castes Category students who have Secured Top Ranks at the State and District Levels in Gujarat in Standard X &amp;amp; XII are given cash prizes. Cash prizes are awarded to the first three students who secure the highest ranks in both Standard X and Standard XII across all streams.\n",
        "benefits_md": "> **Award/Cash Prizes Details at State Level:**\n\n**Sl. No.****Student’s Rank****Award for Standard X****Award for Standard XII (For All Stream)**1First₹41,000/-₹31,000/-2Second₹21,000/-₹21,000/-3Third₹11,000/-₹11,000/-**Award/Cash Prizes Details at District Level:**\n**Sl. No.****Student&amp;amp;amp;#39;s Rank****Award for Standard X****Award for Standard XII (For All Stream)**1First ₹6,000/-6,000/-2Second₹5,000/-5,000/-3Third₹4,000/-4,000/-",
        "briefDescription": "Under the scheme, Scheduled Castes Category students who have Secured Top Ranks at State and District Levels in Gujarat in Standard X & XII are given cash prizes. Cash prizes are awarded to the first three students who secure the highest ranks in both Standard X and Standard XII across all streams.",
